# Meta Andromeda validates creative-diversification strategy for 2026 ads

**Your concept-bucket ad set approach works WITH Andromeda, not against it.** Meta's December 2024 retrieval overhaul fundamentally shifted advertising from audience-based targeting to creative-driven optimization—and the evidence strongly supports putting multiple creative styles (founder POV, demo, UGC, CGC, walkthrough) inside a single ad set. Andromeda's deep neural networks automatically match different creative styles to different micro-audiences, making creative diversity the primary mechanism for reaching new customer segments. Advertisers who consolidated structures and diversified creatives report **17% more conversions** and **35% lower CPAs**, while those maintaining fragmented accounts with similar-looking ads experienced dramatic performance drops.

