## Optimal creative volume: 8-15 distinct concepts minimum

| Spend Level | Recommended New Creatives | Total Active Creatives |
|-------------|---------------------------|------------------------|
| $0-25k/mo | 4-8 new monthly | 8-15 per ad set |
| $25-100k/mo | 6-20 new monthly | 15-30 per ad set |
| $100k+/mo | 10%+ of ad spend on production | 20-50 per ad set |

Meta's ASC campaigns now support up to **150 creatives** (raised from 50), signaling the platform's intent to reward creative volume. However, quality matters more than quantity: "20 different ads that are really different in style beats 200 very similar ads."

Critical warning from practitioners: don't load 30-40 creatives if budget can't support learning across them. Each creative needs sufficient spend to generate data. The sweet spot for most advertisers is **8-15 genuinely distinct concepts** per ad set, with refresh cycles of 2-4 weeks for top performers.

